name: I Am Rich x2
description:
!!! IMPORTANT !!!
1. You must resell for double the price, you payed for this artwork 
2. You must keep it max. 24 hours, then you have to offer it again

This piece shows that you are rich, extremely rich. Nobody can afford to buy it.
Even if somebody buys it, you will make a big profit - just a good win/win situation.

Your collection is only the most valuable, if you own this one!

This artwork is one of three in the “I Am Rich” series.
